# CODEOWNERS file for repo-template
# 
# This file defines ownership for different parts of the repository.
# When a pull request is created, the listed users/teams will automatically
# be requested as reviewers for the corresponding files.
#
# Format: [file pattern] [owner(s)]
# Owners can be:
# - @username (individual GitHub user)
# - @organization/team-name (GitHub team)
# - email@domain.com (email address)
#
# Learn more about CODEOWNERS: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for all files in the repository
# The last matching pattern has the highest precedence
* @Chris-Wolfgang

# Documentation files
